-12th-2024-kilkenny-ie-bruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-band-review.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/may-12th-2024-kilkenny-ie-bruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-band-review.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/may-12th-2024-kilkenny-ie-bruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-band-review.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/may-12th-2024-kilkenny-ie-bruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-band-review.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/may-12th-2024-kilkenny-ie-bruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-band-review.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 57558, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/01/kingdom-of-days-july-1-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 22587, "position": 4}, "title": "July 1", "author": "Ken", "date": "July 1, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "The Born in the U.S.A. Tour gets underway, and the Reunion Tour comes to a close. Plus: catch guest spots with Brian Wilson and La Bamba, and listen to the E Street Band tinker with \"New York City Serenade\" during a Darkness soundcheck.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cover_14.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cover_14.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cover_14.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cover_14.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/cover_14.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 61048, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/10/05/kingdom-of-days-october-5-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 22587, "position": 5}, "title": "Kingdom of Days: October 5", "author": "Ken", "date": "October 5, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: Bruce releases Tunnel of Love, his eighth studio album. Plus: Bruce performs on SNL (and winds up in the doghouse during rehearsals), an epic Neil Young guest appearance, and much more.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/tunnel-of-love.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/tunnel-of-love.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/tunnel-of-love.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/tunnel-of-love.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/tunnel-of-love.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}], "_links": {"self": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/22587", "targetHints": {"allow": ["GET"]}}], "collection": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}], "about": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}], "author": [{"embeddable": true, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/users/1"}], "replies": [{"embeddable": true, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=22587"}], "version-history": [{"count": 11, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/22587/revisions"}], "predecessor-version": [{"id": 68949, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/22587/revisions/68949"}], "wp:featuredmedia": [{"embeddable": true, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/media/22659"}], "wp:attachment": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=22587"}], "wp:term": [{"taxonomy": "category", "embeddable": true, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/categories?post=22587"}, {"taxonomy": "post_tag", "embeddable": true, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/tags?post=22587"}], "curies": [{"name": "wp", "href": "https://api.w.org/{rel}", "templated": true}]}}